-- SandRidge to Sell Permian Assets for $2.6 Billion to Sheridan
-- B y   T i n a   D a v i s
-- 2012-12-19T21:16:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-19/sandridge-to-sell-permian-assets-for-2-6-billion-to-sheridan.html
SandRidge Energy Inc. (SD)  agreed to sell
assets in the Permian Basin to closely held Sheridan Production
Partners II for $2.6 billion in cash.  The properties sold produced the equivalent of about 24,500
barrels of oil a day at the end of the third quarter, Oklahoma
City-based SandRidge said in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tina Davis at 
 tinadavis@bloomberg.net  